snippet.title: Surfer's Paradise But Danger Below! for the Atari 2600
snippet.description: Meh surfing game with 2 "screens". In the first one you have to do stunts to get points and in the other one, which happens if you fall of your surfboard, you have to get back to your board, while avoiding jellyfishes.
